    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting with my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, she's a total beauty! This car is in truly pristine condition\u2014honestly, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied it since day one, keeping it tucked away in the garage and making sure it stays spotless. It drives like an absolute dream and has been loved every mile of the way. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s essentially brand new, you've found it! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 47500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
