    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of the marque, featuring the legendary S54 inline-six engine with independent throttle bodies and a precision-tuned double VANOS system. The mechanical integrity is absolute; the subframe has been proactively reinforced to maintain structural rigidity, and the Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox offers tight, tactile throws. Power is delivered through a factory limited-slip differential, ensuring optimal traction and corner-exit stability. The suspension retains its original geometry with fresh bushings and dampers, providing the signature communicative steering rack feel these chassis are known for. Every fluid has been analyzed, and the valve clearances are strictly within spec. This is a turn-key, investment-grade driver for the enthusiast who demands mechanical perfection.",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "2021 Sedan. Showroom condition. No scratches or mechanical issues. Spotless interior. Full service history available.",
      "price": 43500.0,
