    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle in true collector-grade condition. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, ensuring the exterior retains its deep, mirror-like factory luster with absolutely no chips, swirls, or imperfections. The interior is equally breathtaking, featuring supple leather upholstery that shows no signs of bolster wear and still carries a hint of that showroom-new aroma. Every switch, dial, and electronic feature functions with crisp precision. Under the hood, the engine bay is spotless, reflecting a rigorous maintenance schedule performed exclusively by certified technicians. This vehicle drives with the same tight, responsive performance it had on day one. For the buyer who demands perfection and a complete service history, this is the definitive example of the model.",
      "price": 48500.0,
