    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You've got to see this beauty. It's honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014absolutely spotless and runs like a dream! I've babied this car since day one, always kept it garaged and perfectly maintained. If you're looking for a ride that feels brand new, this is definitely the one. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
