    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a concours-level E46 M3, a definitive masterclass in naturally aspirated engineering. At its heart lies the S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing, delivering a razor-sharp 8,000 RPM redline. This example is mechanically flawless, with documented rod bearing replacement, Beisan Systems VANOS bulletproofing, and a reinforced rear subframe to ensure chassis integrity. The 6-speed Getrag manual transmission provides precise throws, coupled with a factory limited-slip differential for optimal power delivery. The suspension geometry remains true to factory specifications, offering the communicative feedback and lateral grip this platform is renowned for. This is a turn-key, investment-grade specimen for the technical purist.",
